  "id": "RAW_d1b0ca",
  "title": "马斯克推最强 Grok 4！人类终极测试干翻 OpenAI，包月费超 2 千元",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4MTQ4NjQzMw==&mid=2652785615&idx=1&sn=22a5e69c2b93a6c0b7dfced2c7518071",
  "date": "2025-07-10 07:39:00",
  "author": "智东西",
  "siteName": "智东西",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 20px;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: top;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4255555555555556\" data-w=\"900\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=22032c5e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLiaxuN6DcAGDShicbpwybuhKSndhTQ2K66cGKCW8FiaJhpv58za8o2W2EyoB9bx2JfCFInD1tZLcktKQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 15px 8px 35px;\">\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: normal;font-size: 15px;padding: 0 10px;border-left: 3.5px solid #00b0ec;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">决战GPT-5！马斯克抢发Grok 4。</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 7.5px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">作者 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 63px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">李水青</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 35px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">编辑 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 63px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">心缘</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">智东西7月10日报道，今日，马斯克的AI公司xAI发布其最新旗舰大模型</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Grok 4</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">和多智能体版本</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Grok 4 Heavy</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，并推出</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">史上最贵的每月300美元（</span><span leaf=\"\">约合2153元人民币）</span><span leaf=\"\">的AI订阅计划Super Grok Heavy</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在“人类的最后考试”（Humanity's Last Exam）中，Grok 4在无需“工具”的情况下取得了</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">25.4%</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">的准确率，超过了</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">谷歌Gemini 2.5 Pro的21.6%</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">和</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI o3（高版本）的21%</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">配备“工具”的Grok 4 Heavy获得</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">44.4%</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">的得分，优于配备工具的</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 2.5 Pro的</span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\">26.9%</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.524074074074074\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c45e2de2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLiaxuN6DcAGDShicbpwybuhKSx2fgLZcibiclSl9s3qgM80HseNYCE5cTicjmGhKqXBUXQrEeaIzCWAJsg%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲</span><span leaf=\"\">Grok 4 Heavy</span><span leaf=\"\">在Humanity's Last Exam测评中取得第一</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“就学术问题而言，Grok 4在各个学科上都比博士水平高，无一例外。”马斯克在直播中说，“有时，它可能缺乏常识，而且它还没有发明新技术或发现新的物理学说，但这只是时间问题。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5259259259259259\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=54366615&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLiaxuN6DcAGDShicbpwybuhKSgYf8vjINVr2NyvoOFjMovjxRpBjcb5SYQ7YLoZPnUVH6EQicE1C8UQQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲埃隆·马斯克在直播中发言</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">xAI还推出了迄今为止最昂贵的AI订阅计划——</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">每月300美元的Super Grok Heavy</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。订阅者可以抢先体验Grok 4 Heavy，并抢先体验新功能。这些新功能包括但不限于：</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">将于8月推出的AI编码模型，9月推出的多模态智能体，以及10月推出的视频生成模型。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5453703703703704\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=55641384&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLiaxuN6DcAGDShicbpwybuhKSOjLMKU2CE7asNDnHxpZ7iak97ZStbbzZVIuMKuNkCNTxLiasXrweL2TA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">▲</span><span leaf=\"\">每月300美元的Super Grok Heavy正式推出</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">直播结束后，马斯克在X上发文称：“你可以将整个源代码文件剪切并粘贴到Grok上的查询输入框中，然后@Grok 4会帮你解决，</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">比Cursor更好用</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.29907407407407405\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e8cb2530&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLiaxuN6DcAGDShicbpwybuhKSiaWY8b8Cyv9JtdEdxSoBpRDYvVVHCICBOXhtQ6swvZVVtgrXribiceVxQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">▲马斯克在社交平台X上发言</span></span></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">除此之外，xAI推出了</span><span style=\"color: #0f59a4;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Grok 4 API</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。xAI的企业部门仅成立两个月，但它计划与超大规模企业合作，通过其云平台提供Grok。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">近几个月来，xAI不仅拿下100亿美元最新融资，还收购了社交平台X，这也让最新推出的Grok 4成为产业的关注焦点。Grok 4能否成为对打OpenAI计预告今夏推出的GPT-5的有力对手？让我们来一起先睹为快。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 20px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.5px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Grok 4测评赶超OpenAI o3</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.5px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">马斯克：科研能力强过人类博士</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.5px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">马斯克在直播中称，在人文、语言、数学、物理、工程等多个基准测试中，Grok 4都取得了好成绩。“有些人认为AI不能推理，但Grok 4的推理能力可以超越人类水平，比几乎所有学科的研究生同时都聪明。”马斯克说。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">xAI的研究人员称，Humanity's Last Exam测试极具挑战性，总共有2500个问题，包括数学、自然科学、工程以及所有人文学科，问题广泛且都是博士甚至高级研究水平，Grok 4在这些问题上可以得到很好的分数。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Grok 4在无需“工具”的情况下，在“测试中获得了25.4%的准确率，超过了谷歌Gemini 2.5 Pro的21.6%和OpenAI o3（高版本）的21%。马斯克称，在学术问题方面，Grok 4比每个学科的博士水平都要好，现在没有例外。他预测Grok 4最快今年就能去发明新技术了，两年之内就能发现新物理学说。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">在GPQA、AIME25、LCB（Jan-May）、HMMT25等多项测评中，Grok 4都超越了OpenAI o3、Gemini 2.5 Pro、Claude 4 Opus等模型。</span></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5324074074074074\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d1ca1c5d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLiaxuN6DcAGDShicbpwybuhKSDmo5eDA250bWrNsONKfHLnczNKF11QzXozNmzNrdYu95pick2t3zIgA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而在ARC-AGI-2测试中，Grok 4取得了新的最高得分，得分为16.2%。ARC-AGI-2测试是另一项高难度基准测试，包含类似谜题的问题，要求AI识别视觉模式。Grok的得分几乎是排名第二的商业AI模型Claude Opus 4得分的两倍。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5370370370370371\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=60417d05&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLiaxuN6DcAGDShicbpwybuhKSvq5eibaiaxUoLddmNft741yDBFHOhy5Q2sTTmJFWkypgdUawibicRGR1wg%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 20px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.5px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">训练量级达到Grok 2 100倍</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.5px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Grok 4将与人形机器人互动</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.5px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从Grok2到Grok 4，每一次迭代xAI都增加了一个数量级的训练，因此Grok 4的训练量级达到了Grok 2的100倍，这使得智力增长非常显著。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是xAI第一次像预训练一样扩大训练规模。基于拥有10万块H100 GPU的超级算力中心，训练主要包括两种类型：一个是从Grok 2到Grok 3到的预训练，一个是从Grok 3到Grok 4在推理中投入了大量的算力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">谈及幕后，如图所示，当投入越来越多的训练算力，模型开始逐渐变得越来越聪明，最终在没有任何工具的情况下，解决了四分之一的Humanity's Last Exam测试问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5481481481481482\" data